@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
@{par}
  @{b}@{u}Introduction@{uu} @{ub}@{par}

zconnect.library is a shared library for easy processing of headers of
so called ZConnect buffers.@{par}

For those who don't know what ZConnect is: ZConnect is a format like the
one specified in RFC 822 ("Standard for the format of ARPA internet text
messages") - but simply another ;)@{par}

Please note that the definitions of ZConnect are currently only German,
that's why the documentation of zconnect.library is German, too.@{par}

See the @{"zconnect.library autodocs" link "/Developer/Autodocs/zconnect.doc/Main"} for
more details.@{par}

@endnode

